                "invention-title": [
                    "Power system based on cracking hydrogen production and high-low pressure combined injection and operation method thereof",
                    "基于裂化制氢和高低压联合喷射的动力系统及其运行方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a power system based on cracking hydrogen production and high-low pressure combined injection and an operation method of the power system, and belongs to the technical field of power energy. The problem that the ammonia fuel is difficult to apply due to overhigh ignition temperature and pressure is solved. Comprising a plasma catalytic ammonia cracking reforming module and an internal combustion engine cylinder module, the plasma catalytic ammonia cracking reforming module is connected with the internal combustion engine cylinder module, the plasma catalytic ammonia cracking reforming module is used for catalyzing fuel, and the internal combustion engine cylinder module is used for igniting the fuel to do work. According to the plasma catalytic ammonia cracking reforming module disclosed by the invention, ammonia gas with relatively high combustion difficulty is converted into hydrogen gas with a relatively wide ignition boundary in a fuel supply stage in a manner of partially cracking and reforming pure ammonia to produce hydrogen, so that hydrogen-rich ammonia gas with relatively low combustion boundary conditions is formed, and the problem of hydrogen storage and transportation in a direct hydrogen-doped combustion-supporting manner is solved; the application of the ammonia fuel as a zero-carbon new energy in a power device becomes possible."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及基于裂化制氢和高低压联合喷射的动力系统及其运行方法，属于动力能源技术领域。解决氨燃料着火温度和压力过高使其难以应用的问题。包括等离子体催化氨裂化重整模块和内燃机气缸模块，所述等离子体催化氨裂化重整模块与内燃机气缸模块建立连接，等离子体催化氨裂化重整模块用于实现燃料的催化，内燃机气缸模块用于引燃燃料做功。本发明的等离子体催化氨裂化重整模块通过纯氨部分裂化重整制氢的方式，将燃烧难度较大的氨气在燃料供给阶段现场转化为着火界限较宽的氢气，形成燃烧边界条件较低的富氢氨气，并省去了直接掺氢助燃方式的氢气储运难题，使得氨燃料在作为零碳新能源在动力装置的应用上成为可能。"
                }
            ]
